# TDD Examples

Code for a small intro to TDD tutorial.

## Project 1 - Practice using TDD from the beginning of a project

Folder: 01_recommendations

Write a simple product recommendation enginer

## Project 2 - Putting legacy code into test harnesses

Folder: 02_DataStats

Take an already existing codebase and start to break it a part and putting the code into test harnesses.

See the code-through here: http://blog.thedigitalcatonline.com/blog/2017/07/21/refactoring-with-test-in-python-a-practical-example/

